<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        background-color: #1a1a1a;
        font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #e0e0e0;
        padding: 32px 16px;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #242424;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .email-header {
        background-color: #1a1a1a;
        padding: 24px 32px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #ffc107;
      }
      .email-header .brand {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #ffc107;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 32px;
      }
      .email-body h1 {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .email-body p {
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #b0b0b0;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      .detail-table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .detail-table td {
        padding: 10px 12px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
      }
      .detail-table td:first-child {
        color: #888;
        width: 45%;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .detail-table td:last-child {
        color: #e0e0e0;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 28px;
        background-color: #ffc107;
        color: #000000;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: 8px 0;
      }
      .alert-box {
        background-color: #2e2e2e;
        border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
        padding: 16px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #ccc;
      }
      .alert-box.danger {
        border-left-color: #dc3545;
      }
      .alert-box.success {
        border-left-color: #28a745;
      }
      .email-footer {
        padding: 20px 32px;
        border-top: 1px solid #333;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #555;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <div class="brand">TATTOOSPHERE</div>
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <%= yield %>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>Tattoosphere — Trouve ton artiste, réserve ton tatouage.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 4px;">Cet email a été envoyé automatiquement, merci de ne pas y répondre.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>